cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.SE, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with learning distributed representations of edits in natural language and source code, which suggests that it could belong to several sub-categories. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as it deals with natural language processing. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses neural networks to learn representations. cs.SE (Software Engineering) is another possibility as the paper deals with source code edits. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) are also possible categories given the use of neural networks in the paper.
